        "        print(EXCEL_FILE_PATH)\n",
        "        break\n",
        "     \n",
        "   "

        },

      },
      "source": [
        "avg_total_doses = data._TOTAL.mean()\n",
        "avg_population = data.POPULATION.mean()\n",
        "print(\"Average of all doses:\", avg_total_doses)\n",
        "print(\"Average Population accross all cities\", avg_population)"
